---
title: Easy Venison & Beef Bolognese Filo Pie with Portabello Mushrooms
description: When you don’t know what to eat, a pie is a sure-fire way to solve the problem. Classic bolognese flavours are cooked up in a beef and venison sauce with hidden mushrooms to add the comfort factor every pie needs. You can relax now that all your dinner time questions have been answered.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
